data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Spectacular home with oversized rooms and extra rooms for you to entertain! Come see the rooms where several of them have been refreshed with new paint. You will love the supersized game room and media room (the media equipment stays). This home has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a formal living room and formal dining room, a first floor room that can be an office or a 5th bedroom, and many other upgrades. Enjoy cooking with the double ovens and gas stove. Come give it a look. It's waiting on you.
